definition: each other/one another/mutually/fret on the neck of a pipa 琵琶[pi2 pa5] (a fret on the soundboard is called a 品[pin3])
appearance/portrait/picture/government minister/(physics) phase/(literary) to appraise (esp. by scrutinizing physical features)/to read sb's fortune (by physiognomy, palmistry etc)
difference/discrepancy/to differ/error/to err/to make a mistake
to differ from/to fall short of/lacking/wrong/inferior/Taiwan pr. [cha1]

sentences.chinese: 相差半个周期则引起抵消。

sentences.english: It's definitely a change from the slender and nimble image seen during his teenager days in Switzerland.
sentences.chinese: 这和他青少年时期在瑞士时苗条聪敏的形象相差很远。

sentences.english: Although this method does not compare the perfect sexual affection, it is not also far.
sentences.chinese: 虽然这种方法式比不上完美的性爱，但是也相差不远。

sentences.english: It is shown that values computed by conventional formula are largely deviated from the measured data.
sentences.chinese: 试验表明，过去的计算值与实际测得数据相差太大。

sentences.english: The prevalence of scar contractures in the upper extremities was similar to that in the lower extremities.
sentences.chinese: 瘢痕挛缩的发生率在上下肢中相差无几。

sentences.english: The signal amplitude is quite different in the different period.
sentences.chinese: 而同一个信号在不同的时期强度相差悬殊。

sentences.english: Women in these places are far from high-achieving entrepreneurs.
sentences.chinese: 农村妇女和成功的女企业家相差甚远。

sentences.english: The analyses show that for systems of few-degrees-of-freedom, there is little difference between the results of the above two methods.
sentences.chinese: 结果发现，对于少自由度系统来说，两者相差不多。

sentences.english: There must be a "reason" for the chasm between the masses of these twin particles.
sentences.chinese: 这对挛生粒子的质量相差悬殊定有“原因”。

sentences.english: Su and Wen are cousins with an age difference of twenty-two years.
sentences.chinese: 兩人为相差二十二岁之表兄弟，情真意切，知己知彼。

sentences.english: The Moon Light replicates exactly the craters and surface of the actual moon.
sentences.chinese: 灯面上的凹凸与真正的月球表面，相差无几。

sentences.english: However, the molecular mechanism of stay-green underlying different genetic background is quite different.
sentences.chinese: 但由于遗传背景不同，它们滞绿的分子机理相差很大。

sentences.english: Many times, screeners are far removed from the front lines.
sentences.chinese: 许多时候，筛选人与一线人员相差很大。

sentences.english: This varies so much that there's no one answer.
sentences.chinese: 这通常相差甚远，没有唯一的答案。

sentences.english: Nevertheless, the molecular mechanism of stay-green in these mutants is quite different owing to different genetic basis.
sentences.chinese: 但由于遗传背景不同，它们滞绿的分子机理相差很大。

sentences.english: September to May the following year as the frost period, frost-free period is short, significant differences between north and south.
sentences.chinese: 九月至次年五月为霜冻期，无霜期短，南北相差悬殊。
